Vita Nuova's modified copy of ``BETA.2 Build 16'' from Lucent's Inferno Business Unit

This software was originally provided by Lucent Technologies Inc under NOTICE.orig and LICENSE.orig.
It is now being made available under the new licence in NOTICE, by Vita Nuova Holdings Limited,
under an agreement with Lucent on 1 March 2000.

With the exception of new NOTICE files and this README, it is provided here as originally archived,
for historical reference.

It was the first source release received by Vita Nuova Limited, in 1996.

* includes source for emu and os
* there is support for Plan 9
* the tree was received in 1996 but this snapshot includes changes made by VN and others into 1997
